":98833,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>youtube唔係有片破解咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，不過唔係依套routine,,而係普通嘅cardtoon,,依條youtube裏面嘅玩法，根本普通cardtoon唔會玩到，Cardtoon有啲紅到已經變左一個效果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Jo9Zot09rsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJo9Zot09rsA&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8afb3faf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Jo9Zot09rsA</a><br />\n好似原創者有新版本咁，如果你知道秘密你就會知我講緊乜<br />\n<br />\n但係樓主條片嗰個好明顯唔係新版，亦唔係原本玩法，而係一個好賤嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係又扮到係新魔術咁"},{"pid":"cd1a7bdb0946daf21fb646affba735a3655813e0","tid":98833,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:00:58.000Z","msg":"好賤？即係夾好左？"},{"pid":"eeb2c0be1ea4a664781d128519c462fa4f175a6c","tid":98833,"uid":74163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:03:51.000Z","msg":"好似非常盜咁 個評判一早已經俾人催眠左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd8423f1e9cc7991c752e0e152676a791da7f18","tid":98833,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似非常盜咁 個評判一早已經俾人催眠左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839cc40d16770d5b2b0c40d2b5e32be0dbdf25fe","tid":98833,"uid":74163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:19:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1tCXPcDxGvs \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1tCXPcDxGvs%20&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=5e0978a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1tCXPcDxGvs </a><br />\n第一個魔術都好犀利 點解可以知道評判諗緊咩明星？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65a80bb585e7932c7624f9d5a6dcfaeeab421db","tid":98833,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似非常盜咁 個評判一早已經俾人催眠左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係有依啲催眠類嘅魔術嘅，不過多數出現係一啲長show<br />\n<br />\nbtw依個一定唔係"},{"pid":"6c84b8558bc66851c4a986260bb96bf60b589b1e","tid":98833,"uid":69242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75ca344247b9a031bd531fe26378650f9634ae6","tid":98833,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/1tCXPcDxGvs \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1tCXPcDxGvs%20&d=CH2%2BOu%2FXd5cykt%2BSaDfKp2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=5e0978a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1tCXPcDxGvs </a><br />\n第一個魔術都好犀利 點解可以知道評判諗緊咩明星？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n道具黎，不過個魔術師本身都好出名同好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629a3a6adae3563482134da3677af4caf4a2b7c6","tid":98833,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好賤？即係夾好左？</blockquote><br />\n其實夾都唔賤，因為魔術本身可以係一個團隊嘅魔術，只要有娛樂到人就okay,,不過有啲之後都會講明有夾，而佢賤嘅地方唔係到"},{"pid":"3558eb6e63b21873482ad994d07b788d7a82291b","tid":98833,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知會唔會誇張左<br />\n佢應該用某種心理手法 植入左紅心七呢個選擇入Simon 想法到</blockquote><br />\n我都覺</blockquote><br />\nNo"},{"pid":"6fc0745c8bb5418790f086f2a1b35ecc58941a56","tid":98833,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得好睇咪欣賞下算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無必要問到篤</blockquote><br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n態度正確"},{"pid":"bf25b75a0e6b8fd599ae0968c2a3314f66c47e7a","tid":98833,"uid":52735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:40:09.000Z","msg":"成班係到吊人隱<br />\n<br />\n搞錯<br />\n<br />\n對唔住 我都唔講得<br />\n職業道德 唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過可以講 由頭到尾佢都冇換過牌 <br />\n冇植入 冇洗腦 冇暗示 <br />\n就算主持講邊張 佢都可以拎出嚟<br />\n其實唔難 只係考換手 <br />\n你只知道原理可能會有啲失望<br />\n因為真係好簡單<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓上位人兄講可以買嘅道具嚟<br />\n我真係笑而不語<br />\n<br />\n你俾枝筆同副牌嚟 我都整到<br />\n我再賣二十俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五蚊變二十 幾賺得<br />\n<br />\n利申：知原理"},{"pid":"f9191d4acc2934006f5f781d96dab9920f0cf0bf","tid":98833,"uid":24935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:48:37.000Z","msg":"好開心有巴打睇完魔術覺得神奇同驚訝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：做緊有關魔術工作，超過10年魔術年資"},{"pid":"db488a5801d9f060c3ee222361eba33a89a3b24d","tid":98833,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:49:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班係到吊人隱<br />\n<br />\n搞錯<br />\n<br />\n對唔住 我都唔講得<br />\n職業道德 唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm