<br />\n<br />\n認同，但呢個觀點不能用於魔術表演上。<br />\n不拆解表演除左係禮貌外亦係對你自身同表演者既尊重</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道秘密週圍講或者當場拆穿就唔尊重，唔知答案互相研究，呢種行為本身就係魔術既一種進程"},{"pid":"4d57e7ff40f6af1e16ce0ed0bea58fdf5e9305ba","tid":98833,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好開心有巴打睇完魔術覺得神奇同驚訝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：做緊有關魔術工作，超過10年魔術年資</blockquote><br />\n我直頭睇到個下爬都趺埋落地<br />\n就算知道個原理之後有啲都仲覺好brilliant <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想plan下次旅行睇埋magic show"},{"pid":"a77ad4398baa56c54561fc8884db31b78a9c1bc2","tid":98833,"uid":24935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求知慾係人類進步既必須心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，但呢個觀點不能用於魔術表演上。<br />\n不拆解表演除左係禮貌外亦係對你自身同表演者既尊重</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道秘密週圍講或者當場拆穿就唔尊重，唔知答案互相研究，呢種行為本身就係魔術既一種進程</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n歪理當真理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解互相研究答案係進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"f00ee2ee8b10f5653a6f608ebfeb376539418a0e","tid":98833,"uid":66481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好開心有巴打睇完魔術覺得神奇同驚訝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：做緊有關魔術工作，超過10年魔術年資</blockquote><br />\n我直頭睇到個下爬都趺埋落地<br />\n就算知道個原理之後有啲都仲覺好brilliant <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想plan下次旅行睇埋magic show</blockquote><br />\n你上youtube睇David blaine"},{"pid":"c5ca7ccbfe372f79b8e814c663166c96d9be5f9b","tid":98833,"uid":28335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班係到吊人隱<br />\n<br />\n搞錯<br />\n<br />\n對唔住 我都唔講得<br />\n職業道德 唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過可以講 由頭到尾佢都冇換過牌 <br />\n冇植入 冇洗腦 冇暗示 <br />\n就算主持講邊張 佢都可以拎出嚟<br />\n其實唔難 只係考換手 <br />\n你只知道原理可能會有啲失望<br />\n因為真係好簡單<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓上位人兄講可以買嘅道具嚟<br />\n我真係笑而不語<br />\n<br />\n你俾枝筆同副牌嚟 我都整到<br />\n我再賣二十俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五蚊變二十 幾賺得<br />\n<br />\n利申：知原理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n走啦 扮九晒野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f13d178e173acef5cd968f5d83910bd1339671","tid":98833,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，但呢個觀點不能用於魔術表演上。<br />\n不拆解表演除左係禮貌外亦係對你自身同表演者既尊重</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道秘密週圍講或者當場拆穿就唔尊重，唔知答案互相研究，呢種行為本身就係魔術既一種進程</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n歪理當真理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解互相研究答案係進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常理虧者無法反駁時就會聲稱對方係歪理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除非你係只識得學人地現成魔術既魔術表演者（即係台慶藝員學兩堂出黎呃細路果D），否則一個需要創作原創新魔術既魔術家，都好自然會不斷思考其他同業既魔術原理，然後自己加以創新改良或模仿。如果無左呢個過程，魔術既世界就好難有新招式出現。"},{"pid":"85085d917d68673562e7c587c1649520382cf907","tid":98833,"uid":24935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道秘密週圍講或者當場拆穿就唔尊重，唔知答案互相研究，呢種行為本身就係魔術既一種進程</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n歪理當真理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解互相研究答案係進程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常理虧者無法反駁時就會聲稱對方係歪理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除非你係只識得學人地現成魔術既魔術表演者（即係台慶藝員學兩堂出黎呃細路果D），否則一個需要創作原創新魔術既魔術家，都好自然會不斷思考其他同業既魔術原理，然後自己加以創新改良或模仿。如果無左呢個過程，魔術既世界就好難有新招式出現。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係呢個point <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我走黎強姦你目的係想你諗下你既治案防範有無漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n魔術世界每日有都新trick 出現唔洗你操心，但魔術好多時要base on 舊有技巧先有新trick 出現<br />\n就好似數學新方程式都要base on 加減數一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你果個論點歪理係事實你士旦捉個魔術人都會認同，唔係我理虧係你已經ff 到自己一定岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}